## Use a custom block definition
. tests/setup

cat <<'EOF' >"$TEST_INPUT"
Title
=====

Subtitle
--------

Set the variable 'greeting' to "hello".

@@@sh
  greeting=hello
@@@

Use greeting.

@@@ sh
  echo "$greeting!"
@@@
EOF

cat <<'EOF' >"$TEST_EXPECTED"
hello!
EOF

./dram blockdef='^@@@@*' pattern=^sh "$TEST_INPUT" | /bin/sh >"$TEST_OUTPUT"
check
